replies.body:
I like personalising their titles to the champion quotes.

For example, with Aurelion Sol I have:

**As violent as it is breathtaking**. _(a more AP heavy (violent) start than the recommended)_
{{item:1056}} {{item:2003}} {{item:3340}} 

**Naturally.** _(core items, naturally you'd want them.)_
{{item:3027}} {{item:3116}} {{item:3009}} 

**Crude, but potent.** _(Defensive items aren't really that exciting, but are potent.)_
{{item:3001}} {{item:3157}} {{item:3102}} 

**Live through this, and we'll chat!** _(self explanatory, dangerous items.)_
{{item:3151}} {{item:3135}} {{item:3089}} 

**_Almost interesting!_ ** _(Items that are needed, but hardly interesting.)_
{{item:2003}} {{item:2055}} {{item:2139}} 

A little nerdy I know xD
but fun none the less.
Give it a try if you end up making some :P
